K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-1: a'arya pra t'i tya sa muta p'a ra da n'a ma ma h'a y'a na s'u tra /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-3: 'phags pa rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-7: bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i nang na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-8: aar mo ni ga lta bu'i rdo leb la rta thul la sogs pa nyan thos chen po rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-10: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang; lag na rdo rje la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po yon tan rin po che dpag tu med pas brgyan pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-11: mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pa chen po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-13: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa lha rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-14: lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195a-15: dri za'i rgyal po gtsug phud lnga pa dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-0: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug stan las langs te bla gos phrag pa gcig tu gzar nas pus mo g-yas pa'i lha nga ri rab @195b kyi rtse mo la btsugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-1: bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su thal mo sbyar ba btud nas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-3: lha 'di dag ni mchod rten bgyid par 'tshal ba sha stag ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-5: ci nas tshangs pa'i bsod nams 'phel ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-8: tshangs pa dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten na dge sbyong dang bram zer bcas pa'i skye dgu las dge slong dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-11: dge bsnyen ma dag bsod nams shin tu mang du 'phel bar 'gyur ba de lta de ltar bcom ldan 'das kyis de dag la chos bstan du gsol /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-12: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i tshigs su bcad pa bka' stsal pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-13: ye dharm'a he tu pra bha b'a he tunte sh'ana ta th'a ga to hya ba data /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-14: te sh'anytsa yo ni ro dha ae bam b'a d'i ma h'a shra mana /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-15: chos gang rgyu byung de dag gi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-16: rgyu dang de 'gog gang yin pa'ang //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-17: de bzhin gshegs pas bka' stsal te //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-18: dge sbyong chen pos de skad gsungs //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-21: rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi chos kyi sku yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:195b-22: sus rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba mthong ba des de bzhin gshegs pa mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-1: mdo dad pa can gang la la zhig gis mi gnas pa'i phyogs su mchod rten ni skyu ru ra'i 'bru tsam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-3: gdugs ni ba ku la'i me tog tsam zhig byas la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-4: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba chos kyi dbyings kyi tshigs su bcad pa nang du bcug na de tshangs pa'i bsod nams bskyed par 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-5: 'di nas shi 'phos shing 'chi ba'i dus byas nas tshangs pa'i 'jig rten dag tu skye bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-6: de nas shi 'phos te 'chi ba'i dus byas nas gnas gtsang ma'i ris kyi lha rnams dang skal ba mnyam par skye bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas nyan thos de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-8: byang chub sems dpa' de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-9: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dag /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-13: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-15: 'phags pa rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-16: rgya gar gyi mkhan po su rendra bo dhi dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-062-012:196a-17: zhus chen gyi lo ts'a bande ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa ////
